    trash without paying the cost.\n[Your Turn] [Once Per Turn] When your Digimon
    are played or digivolve, if any of them have the [NSo]\_trait, 2 of your Digimon
    may DNA digivolve into a Digimon card with the [NSo]\_trait in the hand. Then,
    that DNA digivolved Digimon may attack."
